title: Grafix Medium Weight Acid-Free 0.057” Chipboard Sheets, Create Three-Dimensional Embellishments for Cards, Papercrafts, Mixed Media, Home Décor, and More, 12 x 12, Natural, 25 Count
description: Medium-weight chipboard sheets: natural. Grafix chipboard sheets come to you completely bare so you can dress them up however you would like. Paint; ink; stamp sand, distress the cover with paper fibers and fabric; stitch; die-cut; layer and even creates a handmade album--the possibilities are endless. Acid-free. The Package contains twenty-five 12 by 12-inch sheets. Imported.
